name: LostThralls
description:
This mod adds the deleted IDs from AoC back into the spawn tables. I don't have the actual data, so I just winged it.

Really use this to get your equipment back and delete these thralls once done. Or you can play with it, feel free to mod it yourself. 

Github source: [url=https://github.com/teella/LostThralls]LostThralls on GitHub[/url]
